quote><br />\n屋企食飯比人斬到一頸血"},{"pid":"ccbba50fa48504025ce2450e048229f757b9cc63","tid":355182,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係有血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西貢又比人斬 SSP又比人斬 去邊度食先唔會比人斬到一頸血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己屋企煮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落街市 超市買都會比人斬</blockquote><br />\n屋企食飯比人斬到一頸血</blockquote><br />\n不滿晚飯無份 老夫斬妻<br />\n　【明報專訊】油麻地昨日發生老夫斬妻倫常血案，揭發一名內地婦人嫁來香港、卻不幸遇上暴力丈夫，多年來為了年幼子女啞忍枕邊人虐待。夫婦昨午因「煮飯無預埋」小故爭吵，有人盛怒下持菜刀由寓所追斬妻子至街上，婦人身中多刀浴血，躁夫則被趕至警方當場擒獲。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgcache.sina.com/?s=D77DS9iaf%2FmWN5KPD9S6eQmWO5GrB8VmfPWGX9q%2FD8GDVQSuT96XC627PR36B8b%2FE626fPGWO6rz%2F8RveNHOT6q6N71nRNmGTsn6OtyygBD1Y4puPvjP%2BAzxU4mrI9lOw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgcache.sina.com%2F%3Fs%3DD77DS9iaf%252FmWN5KPD9S6eQmWO5GrB8VmfPWGX9q%252FD8GDVQSuT96XC627PR36B8b%252FE626fPGWO6rz%252F8RveNHOT6q6N71nRNmGTsn6OtyygBD1Y4puPvjP%252BAzxU4mrI9lOw&h=d458e3bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81ffc41d8b771d883dd063e79638850dd75d4926","tid":355182,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:02:17.000Z","msg":"內地人<br />\nCC台仲唔禁正皮"},{"pid":"8fcb958c9867eb0d9a3772803645a0efc3dc5d8c","tid":355182,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內地人<br />\nCC台仲唔禁正皮</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a703c2ae777dbf53eec9328e401014b52dddd8a","tid":355182,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係有血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西貢又比人斬 SSP又比人斬 去邊度食先唔會比人斬到一頸血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己屋企煮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落街市 超市買都會比人斬</blockquote><br />\n屋企食飯比人斬到一頸血</blockquote><br />\n不滿晚飯無份 老夫斬妻<br />\n　【明報專訊】油麻地昨日發生老夫斬妻倫常血案，揭發一名內地婦人嫁來香港、卻不幸遇上暴力丈夫，多年來為了年幼子女啞忍枕邊人虐待。夫婦昨午因「煮飯無預埋」小故爭吵，有人盛怒下持菜刀由寓所追斬妻子至街上，婦人身中多刀浴血，躁夫則被趕至警方當場擒獲。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgcache.sina.com/?s=D77DS9iaf/mWN5KPD9S6eQmWO5GrB8VmfPWGX9q/D8GDVQSuT96XC627PR36B8b/E626fPGWO6rz/8RveNHOT6q6N71nRNmGTsn6OtyygBD1Y4puPvjP+AzxU4mrI9lOw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgcache.sina.com%2F%3Fs%3DD77DS9iaf%2FmWN5KPD9S6eQmWO5GrB8VmfPWGX9q%2FD8GDVQSuT96XC627PR36B8b%2FE626fPGWO6rz%2F8RveNHOT6q6N71nRNmGTsn6OtyygBD1Y4puPvjP%2BAzxU4mrI9lOw&h=3b402113&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}